  "title": "Sales Advisors (Gold & Jewellery) | $2.5K - $3.5K + Incentives",
  "description": "<p>Ready to elevate your retail career with one of Asia’s most prestigious jewellery brands?<br />Our client is expanding their team — and we’re looking for passionate, polished, and customer-focused <strong>Sales Advisors</strong> to join.</p><p>🛍️ <strong>Your Role – Sales Advisor</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver a <strong>luxury shopping experience</strong> and build long-term client relationships</p></li><li><p>Advise customers on gold & jewellery products with confidence</p></li><li><p>Drive sales through upselling, cross-selling & clienteling</p></li><li><p>Maintain high standards of store presentation & visual merchandising</p></li><li><p>Support daily store operations: cashiering, inventory, reporting</p></li><li><p>Uphold grooming standards and represent the brand with pride</p></li></ul><p>🎯 <strong>What We Look For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong retail background (luxury preferred but NOT required)</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills and strong customer-service approach</p></li><li><p>Track record of meeting or exceeding sales targets</p></li><li><p>Strong clienteling skills</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>44 hours per week; 5 days</p></li><li><p>Locations: Jewel Changi, Changi Airport, Serangoon, Jurong Point</p></li></ul><p>✨ Why Join Us?</p><ul><li><p>Be part of an internationally renowned jewellery brand</p></li><li><p>Attractive commission structure – earn more the harder you sell</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities within a leading luxury group</p></li></ul><p>💎 <strong>Interested? Apply now and shine with us!</strong><br />Please submit your updated resume <strong>with a profile photo</strong> for faster shortlisting to:<br />📧 <a href=\"mailto:deborah@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>deborah@crew.sg</strong></a><br /></p><p><strong>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</strong><br />Crew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence No: <strong>24C2435</strong></p>",
